Package: tradisanalyseR
Type: Package
Title: A collection of scripts to analyse TraDIS output from the Bio-TraDIS analysis pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Geraldine Sullivan
Maintainer: Geraldine Sullivan <geraldine.sullivan@hdr.mq.edu.au>
Description: A collection of scripts to analyse TraDIS output from the Bio-TraDIS analysis pipeline.
    Can currently structure Bio-TraDIS csvs and corresponding EMBL files (structure_embl()) and
    plot log fold changes for a gene list.
